Package fs.log

Interface Summary
LogHistoryListener This interface defines a listener which listens for changes in a LogHistoryModel.
LogHistoryModel The basic interface that should be available by every data model representing a LogHistoryWindow.
 

Class Summary
AbstractLogHistoryModel This class represents the basic functionality of the model of a log history window.
DefaultLogHistoryWindowModel Provides the standard model implementation for LogHistoryWindow.
LevelAnnotatedMessage This is class wraps a tupel of a string (that represents a formatted log message) and an org.apache.log4j.Level.
